    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230530/extras/81c2c906f82326231e3b8f80a391b07b.avif?t=1770073374\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your father’s beloved hotel is now yours to protect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As time passes and debts grow, Hotel Clover now stands under a dangerous shadow. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What was once vibrant with warmth and life now awaits you to guide it back, letting its life bloom once more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you save the precious hotel your father left behind? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perhaps, you'll find something more along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230530/extras/7e14e0bd964d3601bf2f02b90c752b24.avif?t=1770073374\" width=620 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Manage your hotel.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy furniture, decorate the lobby and rooms, and attract more guests.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230530/extras/c1f319cf296ceb7d7a4ebd83363b5301.avif?t=1770073374\" width=620 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Please your guests.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offer the right services to earn wealth and fame.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230530/extras/9c252cb9150dd8e0d4716e6b36cb8b9d.avif?t=1770073374\" width=620 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Build special relationships.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with guests, uncover their secrets, and grow closer.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230530/extras/bceac123aff8f08e0ed63085ac04b4db.avif?t=1770073374\" width=620 height=133 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Act and grow.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step beyond the hotel, explore activities, and work toward your goals.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p>",
